  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK932">
<l>oṉṟeyti nūṟiḻakkuñ cūtarkku muṇṭāṅkol </l>
<l>naṉṟeyti vāḻvatō rāṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is there indeed a means of livelihood that can bestow happiness on gamblers who gain one and lose a hundred ?</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
